Global Pharmaceutical Grade Castor Oil Market Insights
Pharmaceutical Grade Castor Oil Market size was valued at USD 0.91 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.67 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Pharmaceutical Grade Castor Oil Market Overview
The global pharmaceutical grade castor oil market has seen substantial growth over recent years, with a market size valued at approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2024. This growth is driven by increasing applications in pharmaceuticals, cosmetics, and the growing awareness of the oil's health benefits. The pharmaceutical-grade castor oil market is expected to grow at a CAGR of 5.5% from 2024 to 2030. North America holds the largest share of the market, followed by Europe and the Asia Pacific. The demand for eco-friendly and natural alternatives in the healthcare and cosmetic sectors is also pushing the market forward.

